    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> Nonio Asprenate <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Aquila Iuliano co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Lucius Fenestella hospitium <lb n="4"/>fecit cum senatu populoque civitatis <lb n="5"/>Aratispitanae eumque <note>sic</note> liberos poste<lb break="no" n="6"/>rosque eorum in fidem clientelam<lb break="no" n="7"/>que suam liberorum <expan><abbr>posterorumq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>suorum recepit <lb n="9"/>egit <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Vibius Rufinus <expan><abbr>mag</abbr><ex cert="low">istratus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Hospitium-Vertrag. Bronzetafel; darüber Giebel mit Akroterien. Z. 1/2: co(n)s(ulibus) steht am rechten Rand zwischen Z. 1 und 2.</p>
            </div>
